16:11.138 --> 16:12.539
but yours sure could no.

16:12.572 --> 16:13.440
No.

16:13.473 --> 16:15.508
We like an open yard.

16:15.542 --> 16:18.378
It's more neighborly.

16:18.411 --> 16:20.847
Uh-- hold it.

16:20.880 --> 16:25.352
See-- see, the thing
of it is, um, Dan--

16:25.385 --> 16:26.886
