17:27.013 --> 17:28.115
You don't understand.

17:28.148 --> 17:40.527
It's not that we want to
look, we can't help it.

17:40.560 --> 17:41.828
You can't help it?

17:44.664 --> 17:46.833
Well, we don't want to
offend you or anything.

17:46.866 --> 17:48.435
