18:12.692 --> 18:17.364
Perhaps, if we were
younger and more attractive

18:17.397 --> 18:19.632
we wouldn't be having that talk.

18:19.666 --> 18:23.603
Well, yeah, probably not
for a couple more weeks.

18:23.636 --> 18:26.206
I feel sorry for you people.

18:26.239 --> 18:32.412
Nudity is our chosen lifestyle,
but you can't help yourselves.

18:32.445 --> 18:35.482
You're compulsive,
sick, perverts.

18:38.351 --> 18:42.222
Well, it's not that
easy not to look.

18:42.255 --> 18:45.124
